De_rotterdam

There are 2 bomb targets in this scenario.

Rotterdam Docks are being targeted by a Terrorist Faction.
The Ransom demands were not met, and it is expected that they will attempt to destroy the Main Office and control room for shipping (site A),
OR they will target the company's warehouse (site cool.gif.

Original CS/HL1 version by:
Rob Smolders
(Thank you Rob for the original concept of this map)
